OL,5, Parents who buy a puppy for Christmas  
OL,6, could be funding serious organised     
OL,7, crime in Scotland, the Crown Office has
OL,8, warned.                                
OL,10,FIt says puppy farming is a source of   
OL,11,Frevenue for gang networks and that     
OL,12,Fpeople should not buy a pet from       
OL,13,Funauthorised breeders.                 
OL,15,FThe trade is often carried out through 
OL,16,Fonline platforms, such as Gumtree, free
OL,17,Fads and Pets4Homes.                    
OL,19,FThe market for illegally traded puppies
OL,20,Fis believed to be worth #13m.          
